<br>
The there is a bug... if you hand a pet a weapon faster than the weapon in its primary hand, it will equip the faster weapon in the primary hand.  SInce it now has two weapons in inventory, marked as 1 handed, it will dual weild them.  However, the spear will not move to the second hand, as it is primary only... so the faster 1h weapon get moved to the secondary hand as well... destroying the spear and duping the faster weapon...<br>
<br>
This can be seen more easily at 39, with the sword of runes (the only summonable slower weapon)... you can equip a spear, and then a sword, and the sword will be in the secondary hand. <p>Moghedan Carns,<BR>
